Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface public interface Receiver
A receiver of Transmittable messages with similar function to a Consumer, a sink, a callback or a target.

If the isReceiving() method returns true, then a call to receive(Transmittable) will result in a call to onReceive(Transmittable).

jonathanl (shibo)
